item.title: Ninja Kids Official Video
item.description:
Ninja Kids Official Video

Join us as we celebrate the closing of the first year of the Ninja Kids program in Peterborough. Since September 2015, the program has grown 400% and is constantly growing. Please share this video and visit www.ninjakids.ca to learn more. You can register at the Athletics Centre at Trent, but hurry because the classes fill quickly.
